    • Method Detail

      • onUserGeneratedContent

        java.lang.String onUserGeneratedContent(int type,
                                      java.lang.String content)
        Will be called when a user has generated content and wants to post this to your GetSocial community.
        Implementing this callback allows you to verify the content adheres to your standards or modify/refuse the content if it does not.
        Parameters:
        type - The content type GetSocial.CONTENT_TYPE_ACTIVITY, GetSocial.CONTENT_TYPE_COMMENT, GetSocial.CONTENT_TYPE_PRIVATE_CHAT_MESSAGE, GetSocial.CONTENT_TYPE_GROUP_CHAT_MESSAGE or GetSocial.CONTENT_TYPE_PUBLIC_CHAT_MESSAGE.
        content - The content to approve.
        Returns:
        The approved content to send or null if the content should not be sent.
